    <item>
      <title>中国经济放缓对欧洲企业利润造成越来越大的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/china-s-slowdown-is-taking-a-rising-toll-on-european-profits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从奢侈品品牌到汽车制造商，欧洲企业都受到了中国经济放缓的冲击，而那些严重依赖中国需求的企业将面临更多麻烦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/china-s-slowdown-is-taking-a-rising-toll-on-european-profits</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
